  <h2 id="dos-dont" class="vf-u-margin--0 vf-u-padding__top--400 vf-search-client-side--no-index">Do / Don't</h2>
  <h3>Do</h3>
  <ul class="vf-list vf-list--unordered">
    <li class="vf-list__item">Define clear and measurable LRO standards</li>
    <li class="vf-list__item">Conduct regular audits with follow-through</li>
    <li class="vf-list__item">Monitor real-user performance continuously</li>
    <li class="vf-list__item">Assign accountability clearly across teams</li>
    <li class="vf-list__item">Continuously improve governance mechanisms</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Don't</h3>
  <ul class="vf-list vf-list--unordered">
    <li class="vf-list__item">Treat compliance as one-time activity</li>
    <li class="vf-list__item">Rely on manual checks only</li>
    <li class="vf-list__item">Ignore accessibility and inclusivity gaps</li>
    <li class="vf-list__item">Delay remediation of known high-impact issues</li>
  </ul>

